The refrigeration compartment of the best French door refrigerator has multiple storage options. Full-width, adjustable, sliding or tilting, spill-proof shelves can accommodate pizza boxes, sheet cakes and leftovers. Constructed from thick tempered glass, the versatile shelves allow the owner to customize the storage area for their own food storage needs.","In general, the refrigeration compartment has one or more humidity-controlled crisper drawers that keep fruit fresh and vegetables crisp. A full-width deli bin preserves luncheon meats and cheeses. Moreover, these types of side-by-side refrigerators usually come with in-the-door bins for storing eggs, butter dishes and condiments. In most models, the appliance has a gallon-sized area for storing milk, juices and other large containers. The temperature of this dairy section is often a few degrees cooler than the rest of the refrigeration compartment.","Some bottom-freezer refrigerators come equipped with external water and ice dispensers. These dispensers deliver great tasting, cold, filtered water and ice cubes in seconds. <br/><br/>"]},"id":"fb063bc2-e9bf-4163-9727-49f107e423f9","type":"text"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Commonly, the French door refrigerator has an external LCD control panel. This electronic digital touch-pad is intuitive and easy to use. Through the control panel, owners can customize the bottom-freezer refrigerator&#39;s settings. Configurable options include temperature, humidity, dispenser settings and more.","The Whirlpool Corporation makes side-by-side refrigerators, traditional refrigerator freezers and is the leading innovator and manufacturer of French door refrigerators. Brands under the Whirlpool umbrella include Whirlpool, Maytag, KitchenAid, Jenn-Air, Amana, Bauknect, Brastemp, Consul, Roper and Gladiator. <br/><br/>"]},"id":"e2553300-a5ed-4c67-85be-2e353d178922","type":"text"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Whirlpool has delivered their side-by-side refrigerators, refrigerator freezers and o